---
const curves = [
	{
		id: 'sigmoid',
		label: 'Sigmoid',
		color: '#d66c2f',
		path: 'M30 170 C70 170, 95 165, 118 148 S158 108, 200 100 S242 92, 282 52 S330 30, 370 30',
	},
	{
		id: 'relu',
		label: 'ReLU',
		color: '#2f6b5f',
		path: 'M30 170 L200 170 L370 30',
	},
	{
		id: 'gelu',
		label: 'GELU',
		color: '#5d5fef',
		path: 'M30 172 C88 171, 108 170, 132 163 S170 135, 196 101 S236 62, 275 45 S326 34, 370 30',
	},
];
---

<figure class="diagram">
	<svg viewBox="0 0 400 220" role="img" aria-labelledby="activation-curves-title">
		<title id="activation-curves-title">Comparison of sigmoid, ReLU, and GELU activation curves</title>
		<defs>
			<marker
				id="arrow"
				viewBox="0 0 10 10"
				refX="8"
				refY="5"
				markerWidth="6"
				markerHeight="6"
				orient="auto-start-reverse"
			>
				<path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="rgba(22, 33, 29, 0.55)"></path>
			</marker>
		</defs>

		<rect x="0" y="0" width="400" height="220" rx="24" fill="rgba(255, 251, 245, 0.9)"></rect>
		<path d="M30 190 H375" stroke="rgba(22, 33, 29, 0.22)" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrow)"></path>
		<path d="M200 195 V20" stroke="rgba(22, 33, 29, 0.22)" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrow)"></path>
		<text x="360" y="208" class="axis-label">x</text>
		<text x="210" y="24" class="axis-label">y</text>

		{
			curves.map((curve) => (
				<g>
					<path
						d={curve.path}
						fill="none"
						stroke={curve.color}
						stroke-width="6"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						opacity="0.96"
					></path>
				</g>
			))
		}

		<g class="legend">
			{
				curves.map((curve, index) => (
					<g transform={`translate(36 ${34 + index * 22})`}>
						<rect width="14" height="14" rx="4" fill={curve.color}></rect>
						<text x="22" y="12">{curve.label}</text>
					</g>
				))
			}
		</g>
	</svg>
	<figcaption>
		Sigmoid compresses to a bounded S-curve, ReLU hard-clips negatives to zero, and GELU applies a
		smoother gating behavior.
	</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
	.diagram {
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	svg {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
	}

	.axis-label,
	.legend text {
		font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
		font-size: 12px;
		fill: rgba(22, 33, 29, 0.75);
	}

	figcaption {
		margin-top: 0.8rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
</style>
